    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Septi<lb break="no" n="2"/>mius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Ni<lb break="no" n="3"/>ger <expan><abbr>Co</abbr><ex>llina</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Antio</abbr><ex>chia</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan> XV <expan><abbr>Ap</abbr><ex>ollinaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>XXLV <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XI <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex cert="low">ibertus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex cert="low">atrono</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zeile 2: MI-Ligatur; Zeile 3: TI-Ligatur; kleine O, in C eingeschrieben sowie am Zeilenende; Zeile 4: MIL-, AN-Ligatur; Zeile 5: XX-, TI-Ligatur. Zeile 7 befindet sich im Relieffeld unterhalb des Inschriftfeldes unter einem spitzkegeligen Helm. Im Relieffeld noch Schanzkorb (cophinus), dolabra, ascia. Hild; Krüger; Vorbeck; Mosser; Betz im Kommentar zu Zeile 7: l(ibertatis) p(ileus). Beide Lesarten sind denkbar. (B): Z. 7: AE 1937: fehlt; Betz; Krüger; Vorbeck; Mosser: fehlt, im Kommentar angegeben.</p>
            </div>
